# Design Tokens

Tokens live in two places — both are the source of truth, derived from Figma:

1. **`tailwind.config.ts`** — full extended theme: colors, spacing, fontSize, borderRadius, boxShadow, blur, maxWidth, screens
2. **`src/app/globals.css`** — CSS variables for Shadcn theming (`:root` / `.dark`) and `@theme inline` token aliases

The CSS file loads the config via `@config "../../tailwind.config.ts"`.

