## Rules

- Never use raw hex colors inline; always use Tailwind token classes
- `amber` is reserved exclusively for the "AWS" brand highlight
- For new spacing values, add to `tailwind.config.ts` — not as arbitrary `[px]` values
- Section headings use a slate accent bar prefix: `<div className="h-[2px] w-8 bg-slate-accent" />`
- Use `slate-dark` for light mode accent text, `slate-light` for dark mode (e.g., `text-slate-dark dark:text-slate-light`)
